{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body scrub, specially designed to cleanse and exfoliate the skin gently, to remove dead skin cells and revitalise your body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), wheat germ oil (moisturising), organic extracts of birch leaf (purifying), lavender (soothing) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to damp skin. In circular movement massage in gently. Rinse off thoroughly. On contact with water and by gently massaging in, the scrub transforms into a nourishing lotion that can be washed off easily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Decyl Glucoside*, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Citric Acid*, Betaine*, Xanthan Gum*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (74,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901064843591,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml-231547.webp?v=1739897173","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}